## <a id="reqs"></a>Requirements

Wavefront by VMware Nozzle for Pivotal Platform has the following requirements:

+ Read-only administrative access to the Doppler Firehose and Cloud Controller.
+ A Wavefront account and API token.
+ A Pivotal Platform Quota with at least 8G of available memory.

